com.github.jsontemplate.valueproducer

接口 IValueProducer<T extends JsonNode>

  • 类型参数:
    T - the type of json node expected to be produced
    所有已知实现类:
    AbstractValueProducer, Base64ValueProducer, BooleanValueProducer, ConcatStringProducer, FloatValueProducer, IntegerValueProducer, Ipv6ValueProducer, IpValueProducer, Iso8601ValueProducer, MacValueProducer, RawStringValueProducer, SmartValueProducer, StringValueProducer

    public interface IValueProducer<T extends JsonNode>
    All node producers should implement this interface. The node producer produces a json node which can print expected json string.

    JsonTemplate has implemented some basic node producers which can suit most of the cases.

    Other libraries, such as Guava, Apache Commons, JFaker, support powerful data generations. Users are freely to customize, extend, and add their own producers.

    • 方法详细资料

      • getTypeName

        String getTypeName()
        Returns the name of the producer used in the template.
        返回:
        the name of the value producer

      • produce

        T produce()
        Produces a node without any parameter. None parameter indicates producing a random value by default.
        返回:
        produced json node

      • produce

        T produce(String value)
        Produces a node with a single parameter. The single parameter indicates producing a fixed value by default.
        参数:
        value - the single parameter
        返回:
        produced json node

      • produce

        T produce(List<String> valueList)
        Produces a node with a list parameter. The list parameter indicates selecting a value from the list by default.
        参数:
        valueList - the list of enumerated values
        返回:
        produced json node

      • produce

        T produce(Map<String,String> paramMap)
        Produces a node with a map parameter. The map parameter is the configuration of producing.
        参数:
        paramMap - the configuration
        返回:
        produced json node
